  "name": "Callipsos Safety Agent",
  "description": "Programmable safety layer for autonomous AI agents managing DeFi portfolios on Base (other networks coming soon). Validates transactions against user-defined policies (amount limits, protocol allowlists, action restrictions, reasoning quality). Signs approved transactions via Lit Protocol PKP. Users set policies in natural language via Telegram.",
